spec_data.Name: vdsm-hook-httpsisoboot
spec_data.Description:
Let the VM boot from an ISO image made available via an https URL without
the need to import the ISO into an ISO storage domain.
It doesn't support plain http.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 05 Aug 2017 03:25:26 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Allow directly booting from an https available ISO
